RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

01-352. State v. Morrissey.

Cuyahoga App. No. 77179. Reported at 91 Ohio St.3d 1476, 744 N.E.2d 195. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of the cross-appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of the cross-appeal be, and hereby is, denied.
